{'en': {'shortDesc': 'visualization and analysis tool for atomistic simulation data', 'pkgName': 'ovito', 'longDesc': u'OVITO is a visualization and analysis software for atomistic simulation data. Being a single integrated application it covers both the analysis and the visualization of large-scale atomistic datasets produced by molecular dynamics/statics and Monte-Carlo simulation codes. Its name is an acronym for Open Visualization Tool, emphasizing that the software has been designed with flexibility and extensibility in mind.'}}